{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/live_header_banner-resize.png?t=1673346662\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/steampage_wishlist.gif?t=1673346662\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/about_game_banner_for_steam.png?t=1673346662\" /><br><br>Aether is a 2D side-scrolling hybrid-genre game, combining Daily Life Simulation and Metroidvania Action-Adventure. The game is inspired by Stardew Valley, Magicka, Hollow Knight, Terraria, Rune Factory, and Spiritfarer.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/long-life-sim-new-garden-gif-for-steamgif.gif?t=1673346662\" /><br><br>You assume the role of a wizard freshly graduated from the Academy. You are now going to work under the Ministry of Magic in the Starfall Kingdom with a tower on a secluded island as your new home.<br><br>Grow crops, make a potion, fish, cook, craft, fight, help the villagers, serve the kingdom, and unravel the secret of magic and the lost history of Starfall and beyond in Aether.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/long-life-sim-garden-gif-for-steam-2.gif?t=1673346662\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Full Controller Experience.<br></li><li>Hand-drawn 2D high-frame-count animation style.<br></li><li>Customize your own character and express who you are with a wide array of character customization options.<br></li><li>Explore the magical world full of wonders and mysteries. Adventure and many quests await!<br></li><li>Discover spells, abilities, and upgrades, each helping you to venture further into the uncharted lands.<br></li><li>Create your own unique spell combo from more than 24 types of magic and 50+ spells.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/combo.gif?t=1673346662\" /><br><br></li><li>Fight against evil monsters and protect the innocent from corruption.<br></li><li>Plant, brew, fish, cook, craft! All done by magic, the best utility tool ever!<br></li><li>Furnish your tower chambers to your heart\u2019s desire. It\u2019s not a house, but it can be your home too!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/quest.gif?t=1673346662\" /><br><br></li><li>Meet and befriend the citizens of Starfall. Help them with their requests and learn about their stories. Who knows, one of them might one day become your special someone.<br></li><li>Serve the kingdom and fulfill your duty. We all have a part to play, so spare no magical effort!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/king.gif?t=1673346662\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/steampage_wishlist.gif?t=1673346662\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/2022221124_-_ks_folllow_button_on_steam.png?t=1673346662\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1673346662","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/page.bg.jpg?t=1673346662","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1673346662","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1673346662","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full co